{"blogid": "125582562", "writerAge": "码龄1年", "writerBlogNum": "6", "writerCollect": "4", "writerComment": "1", "writerFan": "0", "writerGrade": "1级", "writerIntegral": "67", "writerName": "冰涼", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_125582562.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "132189", "writerRankWeekly": "1063371", "writerThumb": "7", "writerVisitNum": "9436", "blog_read_count": "5888", "blog_time": "于 2022-07-03 16:57:12 发布", "blog_title": "JDK8的下载和安装，以及配置环境变量", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<h1>一、JDK的下载</h1>\n<p><a class=\"link-info\" href=\"https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/\" title=\"https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/\">https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>1、进入JDK下载页面</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"882\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\c1c97743c32e4de2ae30f24b520f82b2.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p> 2、进入下载页面 </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"932\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\c090b4d2859942c9af0e37c42a436f70.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p> 3、下载</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p> <img alt=\"\" height=\"926\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\9bfedcf85e124d31b93fa51de677af81.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<h1> 二、JDK的安装</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>1.双击安装包，进入安装界面，直接点击下一步</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"509\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\1a8019b795334965ade11e7ef4e4fcea.png\" width=\"756\"/></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p> 2.选择开发工具（Development Tools）和指定安装位置，点击下一步</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"476\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\cbfcafbc9548408b9d7a2a85bf02178b.png\" width=\"625\"/></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>3.完成安装</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"476\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\70423125ae814a1d98baccfcea25b7ca.png\" width=\"625\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"476\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\9fefd9685b4b436d94db922642acccf1.png\" width=\"625\"/> </p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"476\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\6830359c07f34520baee3cef9cba46ef.png\" width=\"625\"/></p>\n<h1>三、配置环境变量</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p> 1找到JDK安装的目录的bin目录，在bin录下Shift+右键（或者Win+R，输入cmd进入bin目录），进入命令行界面进行版本使用查看 <span style=\"color:#fe2c24;\">java - version</span> 版本信息</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"393\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\7580994c06fd45debb239ffd1e0f123c.png\" width=\"872\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"356\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\835273c03d6d4f639dbdfcdf3c4f0170.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>        由于java这个命令只能在bin目录下才能执行，我们的java程序却不能每次也都一起放在bin目录下，更多的是希望不管java程序放在电脑上的哪一个位置，java这个命令都能起到它的作用。于是我们需要<span style=\"color:#fe2c24;\">配置我们的环境变量让java这个命令在任何地方都能起到作用。</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2.右键计算机属性，进入高级系统设置，再进入环境变量</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"815\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\08104264a5434221b69222ebc78a5d7b.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p> 3.添加系统变量</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p> <img alt=\"\" height=\"777\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\9bfe4ca0b0b14f93a4c84322be1443ec.png\" width=\"794\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"934\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\3cb7581ba3104155a78f9f5da6defd0a.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>4.在任意界面Win+R，cmd进入命令行界面，输入 <span style=\"color:#fe2c24;\">java -version </span>和 <span style=\"color:#fe2c24;\">javac</span> ，出现<strong>提示信息则配置成功</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p> <img alt=\"\" height=\"639\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\052caa61171d4adab0321e2ca4d65a92.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n</div>", "first_tag": "Java", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 1, "sql": 0, "php": 0, "time": "2022-07-03 16:57:12", "summary": "一、的下载、进入下载页面、进入下载页面、下载二、的安装双击安装包，进入安装界面，直接点击下一步选择开发工具和指定安装位置，点击下一步完成安装三、配置环境变量找到安装的目录的目录，在录下右键或者，输入进"}